<p>Ah, Maureen, I wish I'd known--that's where I just came back from! <img src="smilies/smile.png" alt="smily"> The ironies of life. I appreciate the confirmations. Yes, a face-to-face connection would be lovely, especially as I haven't been very successful at "converting" anyone. Anyone in the San Francisco/Bay Area? Here's to more sharing in this space, Love, Marlowe</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-container" -->







