</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-author-date" -->
<div class="forum-post-template-post">
<p>Thank you for sharing that Marlowe! Really good to hear that you are getting these results. And it really seems like that your results come as result of your practice with focusing your attention. I have such a strong feeling that I would benefit a lot from working more with my attention. I have a tendency to wait, but I must say that I am starting to get a bit tired of just waiting. So thank you for the inspiration...</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-container" -->







<div class="forum-post-template-container">
